                                                                                                                </h5>
                                                                                                                <div class="mkdf-accordion-content ui-accordion-content ui-helper-reset ui-widget-content ui-corner-bottom" id="ui-id-10" aria-labelledby="ui-id-9" role="tabpanel" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">
                                                                                                                        <div class="mkdf-accordion-content-inner">
                                                                                                                                <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
                                                                                                                                        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                                                                                                                <p>At Caring People we intent to welcome back normality to your home .Extended hospital stay mean separation from family, friends, familiar surroundings and routines. Through Live in nursing care our nurses provide:</p>
                                                                                                                                                <ol>
                                                                                                                                                        <li>Symptom control</li>
                                                                                                                                                        <li>Pain Relief</li>
                                                                                                                                                        <li>Counselling and Emotional support to patients and their families</li>
                                                                                                                                                        <li>Medication, including injections</li>
                                                                                                                                                        <li>Care coordination with your consultant doctor and other healthcare professionals</li>
                                                                                                                                                </ol>
                                                                                                                                                <p>If you and your family prefer the idea of medical care at home, our Nursing Professionals would be happy to answer any questions you may have.</p>
                                                                                                                                                <div class="more-info">
                                                                                                                                                        <p>For more information please call on +91 9020 599 599 or email us to<a href="#"> info@caringpeople.in</a></p>
